title: [Patreon Preview] Impressions with Dan Vear
itunes:title: [Patreon Preview] Impressions with Dan Vear
description:
Remember that one dude from Tiktok that did an impression of Jim? Well, his name is Dan Vear and we got him in the studio! And he shuts us all up with his spot-on impressions.

Follow Dan on Tiktok @DanVearComedy to check out his videos and find him performing comedy!

Subscribe to our Patreon at patreon.com/IDKAT for ad free episodes, bonus episodes, and more exclusive perks! Tiers start at just $2!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
